# Pem mobile app (`app/`)

**Product:** **dump → organized actionables + thoughts journal**. Primary routes: **`/inbox`**, **`/thoughts`**, **`/done`**, **`/dump`**, **`/settings`**. Floating mic → dump. No prep hub, no location. See **`pem-thought-organizer.mdc`**.

## TypeScript & components

- **TypeScript strict** — functional components only.
- **Navigation:** **expo-router** — file tree under **`app/app/`** (see repo layout).
- **API:** **`lib/pemApi.ts`** — `createDump`, **`getDumpsPage`** / **`getDumpDetail`** (`GET /dumps`), inbox, actionables, profile, timezone.
- **Real-time:** **`hooks/useDumpInboxStream.ts`** after dump → refresh inbox when extraction completes.
- **Timezone:** **`components/auth/TimezoneRegistrar.tsx`** — PATCH **`/users/me/timezone`** from **`Intl`** after sign-in.
- **Push:** **`PushNotificationRegistrar`** — **`inbox_updated`** → **`/inbox`**.
- **Haptics:** **`lib/pemHaptics.ts`** for primary taps.
- **Brand:** **`constants/theme.ts`**, **`typography.ts`**, **`brand/pem-brand.html`**.

## JSX readability

Prefer named booleans above the return, early returns for loading/error, small child components — same discipline as before.

**Maintenance:** When **routes, UI patterns, tokens, hooks, or API client shapes** change, update **this file** in the same effort. DB/API contract changes often imply **`pemApi.ts`** + **`pem-backend.mdc`** updates too. See **`pem-project.mdc`** — *Keeping `.cursor/rules` in sync*.

**Collaboration:** See **`pem-project.mdc`**.
